  1. <div> element is replaced with a more appropriate element. use <section> instead of <div>. The <section> tag defines a section in a document.
  2. The divs with the image and caption classes are replaced with self-contained content elements. 
      The <figcaption> tag defines a caption for a <figure> element.

  3. use <main> instead of <div> over all elements
    use <figure> instead of <div> for the image
    use <figcaption> instead of <div> for the image caption
    use <details> instead of <div> for lorem-ipsum class
    use <summary> instead of <div> for description class
-->

